                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The tatzlwyrm belches a puff of poisonous vapor into the face of an adjacent creature, which must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:15|traits:damaging-effect] save; the creature takes a -2 circumstance penalty to this save if it's @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Grabbed]{Grabbed} or @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Flat-Footed]{Flat-Footed}.</p>\n<p>The tatzlwyrm can't use Poison Gasp again for 2 rounds.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target takes [[/r {2d6}[poison]]]{2d6 poison damage} and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target takes [[/r {4d6}[poison]]]{4d6 poison damage} and is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 1 minute.</p>"
                },
